<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<link rel="icon" href="images/logo4.ico"/>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>團資料</title>
<style>
.gd2 {
	margin: 0 auto;
	padding-left: 810px;
}

